OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773191773
OL,3,CD-Day veteran to receive MBE at
OL,4,CWindsor Castle
OL,6,FA D-Day veteran who kept the secret of
OL,7,Fthe German surrender until the end of
OL,8,Fthe war is set to be honoured by the
OL,9,FPrincess Royal at Windsor Castle.
OL,11,FBernard Morgan, who celebrated his
OL,12,F102nd birthday in February, will
OL,13,Fattend an investiture ceremony to be
OL,14,Fmade an Member of the Order of the
OL,15,FBritish Empire (MBE).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
