OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773191773
OL,3,CD-Day veteran to receive MBE at
OL,4,CWindsor Castle
OL,6,FHis bravery and service were
OL,7,Fpreviously recognised by the French
OL,8,Fgovernment in 2015, when he was
OL,9,Fawarded the Legion d'Honneur -
OL,10,FFrance's highest military and civil
OL,11,Fdistinction.
OL,13,FThe centenarian was named in the 2026
OL,14,FNew Year Honours list for his
OL,15,Fcommitment to Holocaust and war
OL,16,Feducation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
